- "career runs are a beacon of excellence, surpassing the average career runs of all batsmen" refers to the total runs scored in all matches being greater than the average career runs of all batsmen.

- "shining stars" refers to the most successful batsmen;
- "career runs have soared beyond 5000" refers to batsmen who have scored more than 5000 runs in their careers;
- "illustrious records" includes the names, total career runs, and career averages of these batsmen.

sql:
SELECT name, country, career_runs
FROM batsmen
ORDER BY career_runs DESC;

